All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Achievement
Achievement class represents CodinGame's achievement.
AchievementLevel
AchievementLevel is enum that represents a level of an achievement.
CodinGame
The class to get all Puzzles from CodinGame's API.
Feedback
Feedback is feedback from players who have solved the puzzle.
MinifiedPuzzle
MinifiedPuzzle is a class that represents a minified puzzle in the codingame.com, the class is used when we get all puzzles from CodinGame's API.
Puzzle
Puzzle class represents a CodinGame's puzzle.
PuzzleLevel
PuzzleLevel class is used to represent the level of a puzzle.
PuzzleType
PuzzleType is enum that represents a type of a puzzle.
TitleMap
TitleMap is used to represent the titles of a CodinGame's puzzle.
Topic
Topic class represents a topic of in a puzzle.
TopicCategory
TopicCategory is enum that represents a category of a topic.
User
User class represents a contributor or a moderator of a CodinGame's puzzle.
